                        <interp inst="t18660409-name-465" type="given" value="PATRICK"></interp>PATRICK FOWLER</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">Policeman, R</hi> 204). I was on duty at Blackheath on 30th March—the prisoner was given into my custody on the charge of steal<lb></lb>ing a watch—he said he did not take it.</p>
